### Notemate Backend API Documentation
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@authToken = YOUR_FIREBASE_ID_TOKEN_HERE
@chatId = CHAT_ID_HERE

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}

###

### 1. Create Chat
POST {{baseUrl}}/chats
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "audioUrl": "https://utfs.io/f/your-audio-file.mp3"
}

###

### 2. Get All Chats
GET {{baseUrl}}/chats
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### 3. Get Single Chat
GET {{baseUrl}}/chats/{{chatId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### 4. Create Message (User Question)
POST {{baseUrl}}/chats/{{chatId}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "text": "What are the main points discussed in this recording?"
}

###

### 5. Get All Messages
GET {{baseUrl}}/chats/{{chatId}}/messages
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### 6. AssemblyAI Webhook (No Auth Required)
POST {{baseUrl}}/webhook/assemblyai
Content-Type: application/json
x-webhook-secret: YOUR_WEBHOOK_SECRET

{
  "transcript_id": "test-transcript-id",
  "status": "completed"
}

###
